      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "I will define a function to categorize match outcomes based on home and away scores and apply it to the DataFrame to calculate the percentage distribution of results.\n",
        "\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
